@node       User-Defined Functions
@c --------------------------------------------------------
@subsection User-Defined Functions

``Power users'' of Coot might also like to write their own functions
that occur after picking an atom (or a number of atoms)

@code{(user-defined-click @emph{n_clicks} @emph{udfunc})}

define a function @code{@emph{func}} which runs after the user has
made @code{@emph{n_clicked}} atom picks.  @code{@emph{func}} is called
