@node Crosshairs
@section Crosshairs
@cindex crosshairs
Crosshairs can be drawn at the centre of the screen, using either the
@key{C} key@footnote{and @key{C} again to toggle them off.} in graphics
window or @command{Draw -> Crosshairs@dots{}}.  The ticks are at
